# Vending System CLI

## Overview
The Vending System CLI is a Python command-line application that simulates a vending machine. It handles product selection, stock management, payment processing, and transaction logging.

## Purpose
This project demonstrates core programming concepts such as control flow, input validation, and file handling.

## Features
- Product selection via CLI
- Stock management system
- Payment simulation
- Change calculation
- Transaction logging

## Tech Stack
- Python

## How to Run
```bash
python src/main.py
